C yields adenine through CN-rich photochemistry with AICN-like intermediates.", "reaction_sequence": ["rxn_013"], "key_intermediates": ["mol_004", "mol_011"]}, {"pathway_id": "P8", "name": "Formamide-to-HCN-to-adenine route", "description": "Formamide first decomposes to HCN, then feeds the classical Or\u00f3 route to adenine.", "reaction_sequence": ["rxn_003", "rxn_004", "rxn_005", "rxn_006", "rxn_007", "rxn_008", "rxn_009"], "key_intermediates": ["mol_004", "mol_005", "mol_009", "mol_011"]}, {"pathway_id": "P9", "name": "Cyanosulfidic 8-mercaptoadenine free-base route", "description": "Sulfurized purine chemistry generates 8-mercaptoadenine, which is photoreduced under cyanosulfidic conditions to adenine.", "reaction_sequence": ["rxn_014", "rxn_015", "rxn_016"], "key_intermediates": ["mol_016", "mol_017"]}, {"pathway_id": "P10", "name": "Cyanosulfidic nucleoside-first route with adenine release", "description": "The Xu cyanosulfidic system first yields deoxyadenosine/adenosine, which can hydrolytically release adenine in later prebiotic pools.", "reaction_sequence": ["rxn_014", "rxn_015", "rxn_016", "rxn_017"], "key_intermediates": ["mol_017", "mol_019", "mol_021"]}], "hub_molecules": ["mol_004", "mol_005", "mol_009", "mol_011", "mol_006"], "convergence_points": [{"molecule_id": "mol_004", "incoming_reactions": ["rxn_002"], "outgoing_reactions": ["rxn_003", "rxn_012", "rxn_013"]}, {"molecule_id": "mol_005", "incoming_reactions": ["rxn_003", "rxn_012"], "outgoing_reactions": ["rxn_004", "rxn_009", "rxn_014"]}, {"molecule_id": "mol_009", "incoming_reactions": ["rxn_006"], "outgoing_reactions": ["rxn_007", "rxn_011"]}, {"molecule_id": "mol_011", "incoming_reactions": ["rxn_008", "rxn_012", "rxn_013"], "outgoing_reactions": ["rxn_009", "rxn_010"]}, {"molecule_id": "mol_012", "incoming_reactions": ["rxn_009", "rxn_010", "rxn_011", "rxn_012", "rxn_013", "rxn_016", "rxn_017"], "outgoing_reactions": []}]}, "reasoning": "", "duration_ms": 127801.64384841919, "success": tru